            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of organic synthesis of dyes, rubber, pesticides and the like, and particularly relates to a synthetic method of perchloromethyl mercaptan. The synthesis method comprises the following steps: stirring hydrochloric acid and hydrogen peroxide in a closed system for reaction to obtain a chlorine-containing hydrochloric acid solution, and then adding carbon disulfide for reaction. According to the technical scheme provided by the invention, highly-toxic chlorine is not used as a raw material, so that safety risks caused by transportation, storage and the like of the highly-toxic chlorine are avoided; the target product is synthesized through a water-phase homogeneous reaction and an oil-water two-phase reaction, and the mass transfer requirement of equipment is low; the hydrochloric acid used in the method can be used mechanically through a mature hydrochloric acid concentration process, the chlorine atom utilization rate is high and can reach 100% theoretically, no waste gas is generated in the process, the generated three wastes are only sulfuric acid aqueous solution, and the subsequent treatment is simple."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于染料、橡胶、农药等有机合成技术领域，具体涉及一种全氯甲硫醇的合成方法。该合成方法利用盐酸、双氧水在密闭体系中搅拌反应得到含氯的盐酸溶液，再加入二硫化碳反应即可。本发明提供的技术方案不使用剧毒品氯气作为原材料，从而避免了剧毒品氯气运输、存储等带来的安全风险；本发明通过水相均相反应和油水两相反应合成目标产物，设备传质要求较低；本发明使用的盐酸可通过成熟的盐酸提浓工艺套用使用，氯原子利用率高，理论可达100%，过程不产生废气，产生的三废也仅为硫酸水溶液，后续处理简单。"
                }
            ]
